<head>PATRIOTISM</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">愛國主義</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>LOVE for one's SELF:own STATE.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>The modern keyword 愛國 "patriotic" has an interesting history in China from ZGC-times onwards. 愛國心 "patriotism" comes in a poem by 汪懋麟 quoted in HYDCD.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
